    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、千紗さん、こころちゃん、すずちゃんと\n今度一緒にユニットを組むことになったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ Chisa-san‚ Kokoro-chan‚ Suzu-chan‚ and I\nare going to form a unit together next time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.6498183807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、橋本さんから聞いてるよ\nみんなで合宿して、企画を考えたんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I've heard from Hashimoto-san.\nYou all stayed together for training and brainstorming‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4666666508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.0999999841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです、合宿すっごく楽しかったです！\nそれで、私がセンターに任命されまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ exactly! The training camp was so much fun!\nAnd then‚ I was appointed as the center…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "センターと言えば瑠依ちゃん……演劇なら座長……\nそんな責任重大な役割、私に務まるでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to the center‚ it's usually Rui-chan… if it's a play‚ she's the lead…\nWill I be able to handle such a significant responsibility…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.7771471899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれなら、きっと大丈夫だよ\nライブを観るのを、俺も楽しみにしてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's you‚ Sumire‚ I'm sure you'll be fine.\nI'm also looking forward to watching the live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2666666508,
